{"id":712,"parent_id":702,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":712,"title":"Isaiah 10","subtitle":"","short_title":"Isa.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 10"],[".studySummary",["i","The destruction of Assyria is a type of the destruction of the wicked at the Second Coming—Few people will be left after the Lord comes again—The remnant of Jacob will return in that day—Compare",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/20"},"2 Nephi 20"],"."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.1","order":"02.24.010.45958"},["b","1"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Woe"],"unto them that decree",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"unrighteous"],"decrees, and that write grievousness",["i","which"],"they have prescribed;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.2","order":"02.24.010.45959"},["b","2"],"To turn aside the needy from",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"judgment"],", and to take away the right from the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"poor"],"of my people, that widows may be their prey, and",["i","that"],"they may rob the fatherless!"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.3","order":"02.24.010.45960"},["b","3"],"And what will ye do in the day of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"visitation"],", and in the desolation",["i","which"],"shall come from far? to whom will ye flee for help? and where will ye leave your glory?"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.4","order":"02.24.010.45961"},["b","4"],"Without me they shall bow down under the prisoners, and they shall fall under the slain. For all this his anger is not turned away, but his hand",["i","is"],"stretched out still."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.5","order":"02.24.010.45962"},["b","5"],"¶O",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"Assyrian"],", the rod of mine anger, and the staff in their hand is mine indignation."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.6","order":"02.24.010.45963"},["b","6"],"I will send him against an",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"hypocritical"],"nation, and against the people of my wrath will I give him a charge, to take the spoil, and to take the prey, and to tread them down like the mire of the streets."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.7","order":"02.24.010.45964"},["b","7"],"Howbeit he meaneth not so, neither",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"doth"],"his heart think so; but",["i","it is"],"in his heart to destroy and cut off nations not a few."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.8","order":"02.24.010.45965"},["b","8"],"For he saith,",["i","Are"],"not my princes altogether kings?"],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.9","order":"02.24.010.45966"},["b","9"],["i","Is"],"not Calno as Carchemish?",["i","is"],"not Hamath as Arpad?",["i","is"],"not Samaria as Damascus?"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.10","order":"02.24.010.45967"},["b","10"],"As my hand hath found the kingdoms of the idols, and whose graven images did excel them of Jerusalem and of Samaria;"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.11","order":"02.24.010.45968"},["b","11"],"Shall I not, as I have done unto Samaria and her idols, so do to Jerusalem and her idols?"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.12","order":"02.24.010.45969"},["b","12"],"Wherefore it shall come to pass,",["i","that"],"when the Lord hath performed his whole work upon mount Zion and on Jerusalem, I will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"punish"],["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_12b"},"the fruit"],"of the stout heart of the king of",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_12c"},"Assyria"],", and the glory of his high looks."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.13","order":"02.24.010.45970"},["b","13"],"For he saith, By the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"strength"],"of my hand I have done",["i","it,"],"and by my wisdom; for I am prudent: and I have removed the bounds of the people, and have robbed their treasures, and I have put down the inhabitants like a valiant",["i","man:"]],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.14","order":"02.24.010.45971"},["b","14"],"And my hand hath found as a nest the riches of the people: and as one gathereth eggs",["i","that are"],"left, have I gathered all the earth; and there was none that moved the wing, or opened the mouth, or peeped."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.15","order":"02.24.010.45972"},["b","15"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"Shall"],"the axe",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_15b"},"boast"],"itself against him that heweth therewith?",["i","or"],"shall the saw magnify itself against him that",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_15c"},"shaketh"],"it? as if the rod should shake",["i","itself"],"against them that lift it up,",["i","or"],"as if the staff should lift up",["i","itself, as if it were"],"no wood."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.16","order":"02.24.010.45973"},["b","16"],"Therefore shall the Lord, the Lord of hosts, send among his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"fat"],"ones leanness; and under",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"his"],"glory he shall kindle a burning like the burning of a fire."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.17","order":"02.24.010.45974"},["b","17"],"And the light of Israel shall be for a fire, and his Holy One for a flame: and it shall burn and devour his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"thorns"],"and his briers in one day;"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.18","order":"02.24.010.45975"},["b","18"],"And shall consume the glory of his forest, and of his fruitful field, both",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_18a"},"soul and body"],": and they shall be as when a standardbearer fainteth."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.19","order":"02.24.010.45976"},["b","19"],"And the rest of the trees of his forest shall be few, that a child may write them."],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.20","order":"02.24.010.45977"},["b","20"],"¶And it shall come to pass in",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"that day"],",",["i","that"],"the remnant of Israel, and such as are",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"escaped"],"of the house of Jacob, shall no more again",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"stay upon"],"him that smote them; but shall stay upon the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", the Holy One of Israel, in truth."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.21","order":"02.24.010.45978"},["b","21"],"The",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"remnant"],"shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"return"],",",["i","even"],"the remnant of Jacob, unto the mighty God."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.22","order":"02.24.010.45979"},["b","22"],"For though thy people Israel be as the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"sand"],"of the sea,",["i","yet"],"a remnant of them shall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_22b"},"return"],":",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_22c"},"the"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_22d"},"consumption"],["sup","e"],["a",{"href":"fn_22e"},"decreed"],"shall overflow with righteousness."],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.23","order":"02.24.010.45980"},["b","23"],"For the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"of hosts shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"make a consumption"],", even determined, in the midst of all the land."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.24","order":"02.24.010.45981"},["b","24"],"¶Therefore thus saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"of hosts, O my people that dwellest in Zion, be not afraid of the Assyrian: he shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"smite"],"thee with a rod, and shall lift up his staff against thee, after the manner of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_24b"},"Egypt"],"."],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.25","order":"02.24.010.45982"},["b","25"],"For yet a very little",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"while"],", and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"indignation"],"shall cease, and mine anger in their destruction."],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.26","order":"02.24.010.45983"},["b","26"],"And the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts shall stir up a scourge for him according to the slaughter of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_26a"},"Midian"],"at the rock of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_26b"},"Oreb"],": and",["i","as"],"his",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_26c"},"rod"],["i","was"],"upon the sea, so shall he lift it up after the manner of",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_26d"},"Egypt"],"."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.27","order":"02.24.010.45984"},["b","27"],"And it shall come to pass in that day,",["i","that"],"his",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"burden"],"shall be taken away from off thy shoulder, and his yoke from off thy neck, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"yoke"],"shall be destroyed because of the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_27c"},"anointing"],"."],["div",{"id":"28","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.28","order":"02.24.010.45985"},["b","28"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_28a"},"He"],"is come to Aiath, he is passed to Migron; at Michmash he hath laid up his carriages:"],["div",{"id":"29","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.29","order":"02.24.010.45986"},["b","29"],"They are gone over the passage: they have taken up their lodging at Geba; Ramah is afraid; Gibeah of Saul is fled."],["div",{"id":"30","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.30","order":"02.24.010.45987"},["b","30"],"Lift up thy voice, O daughter of Gallim: cause it to be heard unto Laish, O poor Anathoth."],["div",{"id":"31","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.31","order":"02.24.010.45988"},["b","31"],"Madmenah is removed; the inhabitants of Gebim gather themselves to flee."],["div",{"id":"32","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.32","order":"02.24.010.45989"},["b","32"],"As yet shall he remain at Nob that day: he shall shake his hand",["i","against"],"the mount of the daughter of Zion, the hill of Jerusalem."],["div",{"id":"33","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.33","order":"02.24.010.45990"},["b","33"],"Behold, the Lord, the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, shall lop the bough with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_33a"},"terror"],": and the high ones of stature",["i","shall be"],"hewn down, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_33b"},"haughty"],"shall be humbled."],["div",{"id":"34","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.34","order":"02.24.010.45991"},["b","34"],"And he shall cut down the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_34a"},"thickets"],"of the forest with iron, and Lebanon shall fall",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_34b"},"by"],"a mighty one."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.1a","order":"02.24.010.45992"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/20.1.1-34"},"2 Ne. 20:1 (1–34)"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.1b","order":"02.24.010.45994"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/injustice"},"TG Injustice"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.2a","order":"02.24.010.45996"},["b","2a"],["span.small","OR"],"justice.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/judgment"},"TG Judgment"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.2b","order":"02.24.010.45998"},["b","2b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/4.16.16-18"},"Mosiah 4:16 (16–18)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/38.16"},"D&C 38:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.3a","order":"02.24.010.46000"},["b","3a"],["span.small","IE"],"punishment.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/9.7"},"Hosea 9:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/19.44"},"Luke 19:44"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.5a","order":"02.24.010.46002"},["b","5a"],["span.small","OR"],"Assyria is the rod of my anger, and my wrath is a staff in their hand.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/31.3"},"Ezek. 31:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.6a","order":"02.24.010.46004"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/hypocrisy"},"TG Hypocrisy"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.7a","order":"02.24.010.46006"},["b","7a"],["span.small","HEB"],"did his heart intend it thus."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.12a","order":"02.24.010.46008"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/19.35.35-37"},"2 Kgs. 19:35 (35–37)"],"."],["div",{"id":"12b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.12b","order":"02.24.010.46010"},["b","12b"],["span.small","IE"],"the proud boasting."],["div",{"id":"12c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.12c","order":"02.24.010.46012"},["b","12c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/8.7"},"Isa. 8:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.13a","order":"02.24.010.46014"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/19.23"},"2 Kgs. 19:23"],"."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.15a","order":"02.24.010.46016"},["b","15a"],"All the metaphors in this verse ask the same question: Can man (e.g., the Assyrian king) prosper against God?"],["div",{"id":"15b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.15b","order":"02.24.010.46018"},["b","15b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/boast"},"TG Boast"],"."],["div",{"id":"15c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.15c","order":"02.24.010.46020"},["b","15c"],["span.small","HEB"],"wields, moves."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.16a","order":"02.24.010.46022"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/34.16"},"Ezek. 34:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/15.17"},"2 Ne. 15:17"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.16b","order":"02.24.010.46024"},["b","16b"],["span.small","IE"],"of the king of Assyria (also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.17-19"},"vv. 17–19"],")."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.17a","order":"02.24.010.46026"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.18"},"Isa. 9:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"18a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.18a","order":"02.24.010.46028"},["b","18a"],["span.small","IE"],"Assyria will vanish completely."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.20a","order":"02.24.010.46030"},["b","20a"],"This prophecy extends to the latter days in the",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.21"},"succeeding verse"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.20b","order":"02.24.010.46032"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/4.2"},"Isa. 4:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.20c","order":"02.24.010.46034"},["b","20c"],["span.small","OR"],"lean, rely upon.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/16.7"},"2 Kgs. 16:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.21a","order":"02.24.010.46036"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-remnant-of"},"TG Israel, Remnant of"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.21b","order":"02.24.010.46038"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/30.6.1-7"},"2 Chr. 30:6 (1–7)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/10.3"},"1 Ne. 10:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.22a","order":"02.24.010.46040"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/9.27.27-28"},"Rom. 9:27 (27–28)"],"."],["div",{"id":"22b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.22b","order":"02.24.010.46042"},["b","22b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/israel-gathering-of"},"TG Israel, Gathering of"],"."],["div",{"id":"22c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.22c","order":"02.24.010.46044"},["b","22c"],["span.small","IE"],"even when punishment comes, mercy is available."],["div",{"id":"22d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.22d","order":"02.24.010.46046"},["b","22d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/world-end-of"},"TG World, End of"],"."],["div",{"id":"22e","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.22e","order":"02.24.010.46048"},["b","22e"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/24.34"},"Matt. 24:34"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/1.7"},"D&C 1:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.23a","order":"02.24.010.46050"},["b","23a"],["span.small","IE"],"cause the decreed destruction."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.24a","order":"02.24.010.46052"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/30.31"},"Isa. 30:31"],"."],["div",{"id":"24b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.24b","order":"02.24.010.46054"},["b","24b"],["span.small","IE"],"as the Egyptians did in earlier times."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.25a","order":"02.24.010.46056"},["b","25a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/54.7"},"Isa. 54:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.25b","order":"02.24.010.46058"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/11.36"},"Dan. 11:36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/20.25"},"2 Ne. 20:25"],"."],["div",{"id":"26a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.26a","order":"02.24.010.46060"},["b","26a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.4"},"Isa. 9:4"],"."],["div",{"id":"26b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.26b","order":"02.24.010.46062"},["b","26b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/judg/7.25.19-25"},"Judg. 7:25 (19–25)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.26c","order":"02.24.010.46064"},["b","26c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/14.26.26-27"},"Ex. 14:26 (26–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"26d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.26d","order":"02.24.010.46066"},["b","26d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/14.27.16-27"},"Ex. 14:27 (16–27)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.27a","order":"02.24.010.46068"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.4.3-4"},"Isa. 9:4 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.27b","order":"02.24.010.46070"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/bondage-physical"},"TG Bondage, Physical"],"."],["div",{"id":"27c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.27c","order":"02.24.010.46072"},["b","27c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-messiah"},"TG Jesus Christ, Messiah"],"."],["div",{"id":"28a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.28a","order":"02.24.010.46074"},["b","28a"],"Progress of the Assyrian armies toward Jerusalem is traced; then (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.33-34"},"vv. 33–34"],") the Lord’s action against them is figuratively described."],["div",{"id":"33a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.33a","order":"02.24.010.46076"},["b","33a"],"See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/36?span=36-37"},"Isa. 36–37"],"or",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/18.13?span=18.13-19.37"},"2 Kgs. 18:13–19:37"],"for a fulfillment of this prophecy."],["div",{"id":"33b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.33b","order":"02.24.010.46078"},["b","33b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/haughtiness"},"TG Haughtiness"],"."],["div",{"id":"34a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.34a","order":"02.24.010.46080"},["b","34a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.18"},"Isa. 9:18"],"."],["div",{"id":"34b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/isa/10.34b","order":"02.24.010.46082"},["b","34b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/37.36"},"Isa. 37:36"],"."]]}
